values:
The rain. Change. Life.

I love and hate the way the things in my life collide.

I don't know how to feel about myself right now. I feel like I'm defeated by a mass invisible army. They hack away at my soul and try to get at my heart. I'm slowly being destroyed and not a single person can save me.

Unless that is why this is happening. Strange occurrences set in place by fate. Fix her, they whisper gently. She's changed. Give her light, give her air, give her water. She's a plant that needs to grow a little bit longer. No one can wait for when she finally blossoms, but remember you're the one who holds the watering can.

I'm the bitch.
I'm the bitch??
Fuck you, you arrogant prick.
After all I try to do for you, after I move away to my parents house as if I am on some form of retreat?
Retreat from you maybe.
I'm not dirt on the bottom of your shoe. You need to know that.
Damn this is stupid.
I'm writing to no one and bitching about nothing that will in turn have people judging me.
Win-win indeed.
However should I act? Should I write you a congratulatory letter on a job well done?
I wish that I could take all the things I want to scream at you and shove them so deep into your ear canal so that for the rest of your life all you can hear is my voice shouting the things you've yelled at me.
I am so sick of being second. I never thought of it that way before.
I can't have my own emotions, because you hog all the emotional space for the both us.
You call me a child, and a child I may be, but at least I know where I stand in life.
I have always shown you love, I have always been loyal. Funny you can't repeat that sentence truthfully.
I despise the fact that in the morning, everything will go away. I will only love you again.
I always shall love you, in the deepest and most respectable manner. Well, perhaps not always so respectively ;}
I simply want happiness. I want to change the world for us. I need you to change as well.
Two left turns in life, will only make one right.
See? I've done it already, I've forgotten my anger and turned it into the mushy shit. I loathe what the thought of your face can do to me.
In the end, I still say Fuck YOU.

Life lately has been so fucked up. I told Drew it was going to get bad. I told him about the tooth dreams, then  he had a dream about teeth. Ugh. I mean, it's just so stupid, I don't understand why my mind is the way it is, but I know that everything is now getting better. I need a job like WOAH. I need to make friends that are my age and can party with me. I want to be able to go out and do things. I'm growing up and realizing what people want me to do. I hate society and I don't want to blend into it, but I'm already putting on the camouflage.

Dvaid is coming home. I don't know what to do. It's kind of freaking me out. i had this whole sean tilley thing the other night. I don't know if he really is into me or not though. it would be so cute if he was. I really need to stop calling people. It just gets me into trouble. Itr's ok if I'm overdoing it now bc when david comes back i probably will have no room for anyone else anyways. but i'm on the phone with david, so i'll ttyl :]

I had a great weekend. Hung out with Steve a lot. He's my new friend:) hung out with the new second in command, Taylor. Of course Sara is first in command. I don't exactly know what all of that means, but it's good. I worked a lot. It sucked. I feel kind of bad, b/c when I went and hung out with Steve and I brought Taylor, it was really lame. But we left and I picked up a kitty for taylor. The cat tried to drive, it didn't work very well. Me and taylor had a grand time visiting Ryan at work, we didn't even know he'd be at the drive thru his first time!! we were both very proud....I talked to David. He's taking tests tomorrow...I hope he does well so he can accomplish something in his life.Oh, well, peace.

I love my life. Everything never goes to plan, but of course, it could never be any fun that way. Sometimes, I hate everything here. I hate the world for being cruel and I hate people for being so goddamn spoiled and nasty to one another. But I look around, and when I see all of the love out there, all of the hope and the faith, I can't help but feel it myself. I feel the love and pain and hope and there's lots of things out there that are horrible and mean, and then I think about it. I think about us, and I thank God I'm here. I thank the Lord above who gave me all of this. I'm not a religous person, but when you think about it, you have to believe something great is helping me out. Getting me, getting us closer to our goals. Life is messy and people just have to stop fucking complaining about it, otherwise, when are you going to have time to focus on the things that really matter? Like the people you love, and the things you like to do. Enjoy it, cause you don't know when a chance to live may come around again.

I have been in such a pissy mood lately, not even pissy, just bipolar. I was all laughing and shit in my car and then I found my purse and it was muddy and i started to bitch out at chris. sometimes i scare myself. like lately, i don't even know what has gotten into me, maybe it's my mom in florida and vinnie's sick and i don't know what to do and he has a fever and my dad is sick, so i've been going everywhere for them and i don't know what to do. we have new furniture and i was explaining it to my mom and she started to yell at me and i don't know, she didn't like that it had purple in it. and it's not like she can take it back, because the place is closed, we were literally the last people to pick up stuff from there. i was out with taylor and sean and the highlight of my day was when i drove off the curb to get into a street, thinking it was an exit. I almost peed my pants. that was when my day was good, and we made some pretty cool shirts :)

I am sooo sick of all this shit. I don't care anymore, I really don't. It's just adding stress to my life, I need to get rid of all of the stress. I thought making fun of people would make other people happy, and now my brother says he hates me and then Sara IM's me about other stupid drama bullshit and we get in a fight and she probably hates me, but whatever, it doesn't even matter to me anymore. I don't care. It's time to start new again. maybe I can just coast by for the rest of the year without any complications. David's gone, Sara hates me, Taylor and I are basically exiled because of a private conversation that michael had no right butting into. I'll be fine. Do you know what I've been doing every night before I go to sleep? I go downstairs and eat either a nice bowl of ice cream or popcorn, or any other available snack. Then I take a shower that lasts forever and then I go to sleep and have dreams about whatever movie it was that I was watching. This is my life. The people at the movie store know my name and all about my life. Like the day I knew I wasn't going to see David ever again and then I got pulled over, I was in the Video Vision parking lot and I started to cry and when I went in I was still crying and I told marvin my story and he told me to cheer up and when he gets his only day off in almost a year, he'll take me out, which always makes me laugh b/c I know he's just kidding, but those guys there are better then fucking bartenders. Plus I've known Lillian since I was about 6. Now those are pretty carefree people. I go there at least once a week and rent about 5 movies at a time. I need to find something that'll get my life in more of a routine, I see my self stating to get Obsessive Comulsive again. Yay, that's always fun. i'm tireed and the keys are starting to blur together. Goodnight all of you whom I still think of as a friend:)

A few years ago a mother and a father decided they needed a break, so they wanted to head out for a night on the town. So they called their most trusted babysitter. When the babysitter arrived the two children were already fast asleep in bed. So the babysitter just got to sit around and make sure everything was okay with the children. Later in the night, the babysitter got bored and so she wanted to watch tv but she couldnt watch it downstairs because they didnt have cable downstairs (the parents didnt want their children watching too much garbage) so she called them and asked them if she could watch cable tv in the parents room. Of course the parents said it was ok, but the babysitter had one final request. She asked if she could cover up the large clown statue in their bedroom with a blanket or cloth, because it made her nervous. The phone line was silent for a moment, and the father(who was talking to the babysitter at the time) said.....take the children and get out of the house.....we'll call the police...we dont have a clown statue..... the children and the babysitter got murdered by the clown. it turned out 2 be that the clown was a killer that escaped from jail. if you dont repost this within 5 minutes the clown will be standing next 2 your bed at 3:00am with a knife in his hand.
